title: Sizzling Ko Grabs Halfway Lead at LPGA Event in Korea
text:
Published By: NYTimes Golf - Today 
Lydia Ko carded a blemish-free seven-under-par 65 on Friday to take a one-stroke lead at the LPGA KEB Hana Bank Championship in South Korea ...
